Package: unriddle
Title: Unriddle Complicated Code within a reveal.js Quarto Presentation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Michal", "Lauer", ,"michal.lauer.25@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3294-771X"))
Description: Helpfull package for presentators who want to explain their code
    line-by-line. This package enables you to add simple comment breaks into your 
    quarto chunks, which will then break-up your slide into multiple slides that
    are split line-by-line with the resulting code printed on side.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
